er.send(1) (uploads/sample12_overflow.sol#9)\n	State variables written after the call(s):\n	- counterArray.push(1) (uploads/sample12_overflow.sol#10)\nReference: https://github.com/crytic/slither/wiki/Detector-Documentation#reentrancy-vulnerabilities-4\nINFO:Slither:E:\\Fix\\uploads\\sample12_overflow.sol analyzed (1 contracts with 100 detectors), 5 result(s) found\n');
