moryArrayCreationOverflow\n	- privateCanBeOverridden\n	- SignedArrayStorageCopy\n	- ABIEncoderV2StorageArrayWithMultiSlotElement\n	- DynamicConstructorArgumentsClippedABIV2.\nIt is used by:\n	- ^0.4.26 (uploads/sample11_overflow.sol#1)\nsolc-0.4.26 is an outdated solc version. Use a more recent version (at least 0.8.0), if possible.\nReference: https://github.com/crytic/slither/wiki/Detector-Documentation#incorrect-versions-of-solidity\nINFO:Detectors:\nReentrancy in FundLoop.main(uint256) (uploads/sample11_overflow.sol#7-14):\n	External calls:\n	- msg.sender.send(1) (uploads/sample11_overflow.sol#10)\n	State variables written after the call(s):\n	- counter += 1 (uploads/sample11_overflow.sol#11)\nReference: https://github.com/crytic/slither/wiki/Detector-Documentation#reentrancy-vulnerabilities-4\nINFO:Slither:E:\\Fix\\uploads\\sample11_overflow.sol analyzed (1 contracts with 100 detectors), 7 result(s) found\n');
INSERT INTO `fix` VALUES (8, 1785557673573941250, 'contract sGuard{\n  bool internal locked_;\n  constructor() internal {\n    locked_ = false;\n  }\n  modifier nonReentrant_() {\n    require(!locked_);\n    locked_ = true;\n    _;\n    locked_ = false;\n  }\n}\npragma solidity ^0.4.26;\n\ncontract FundArray  is sGuard {\n    mapping(address => uint) public balances;\n    uint[] public counterArray;\n\n     function main() nonReentrant_  public payable {\n        if (counterArray.length < 100) {\n            msg.sender.send(1);\n            counterArray.push(1); // 增加数组长度\n        }\n    }\n}', NULL);
